The image shows a close-up view of a hand pouring a liquid, likely milk or tea, from a stainless steel container into an orange-colored cup placed on a dark speckled countertop. The liquid is mid-pour, creating some splashes around the cup. The cup has a handle and a pattern on its surface.

This frame shows a close-up of a white or light-colored cup with an orange handle placed on a dark, speckled countertop. There is a stream of liquid being poured into the cup from the left side of the frame. The lighting is dim, creating a somewhat shadowy effect.
